Package: tRexCAP
Title: tRexCAP Carries Out 3D Whole Genome Chromosomal Structure Estimationu U sing HiC Data
Version: 1.0.0
Description: tRex estimates 3D chromosome structure using three Poisson models under Bayesian framework. Truncated Random effect EXpression (tREX) mode, Poisson Random Effects Architecture Model(PRAM), Truncated Poisson Architecture Model(tPAM). A package that uses a divide and conquer strategy and the tREX algorithm as the building block for constructing whole genome three-dimensional structures.
